T1  - Planning Horizons for the Dynamic Lot Size Model with Backlogging
AU  - Blackburn, Joseph D.
AU  - Kunreuther, Howard
Y1  - 1974/11/01
PY  - 1974
DA  - 1974/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.21.3.251
